Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill will allow you to track your Worldnet packages by simply speaking the tracking ID. The skill will also remember the tracking ID. So when you open up the app again it will let you know the latest status of your shipment. You are also able to change the tracking ID.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
